Converts piCorePlayer image to beaglebone-compatible image

Usage: ./convert.sh in_bone-debian-8.6-console-armhf-2016-10-30-2gb.img in_piCorePlayer3.02.img ./out_bbbCorePlayer3.02.img

P.S: Make sure to run it as-root or in fakeroot -> That is needed to retain file ownerships

CREDITS:
TinyCore/PiCore: tinycorelinux.net
piCorePlayer: sites.google.com/site/picoreplayer
depmod.pl: busybox.net
